    "name": "Hemolysis output comparison verification requirement",
    "description": "For MRL 5 Class III VAD hemolysis prediction, the output comparison credibility factor must be substantiated by experimental-validation against physical bench-top or in-vitro hemolysis measurements. Literature survey or simulation-only evidence is not sufficient to satisfy this requirement.",
