        "description": "Systematic review of published hemolysis prediction studies for centrifugal blood pumps. Covered 2005–2024 literature; extracted predicted versus reported hemolysis indices from 23 peer-reviewed sources. No new physical experiments were conducted."
      },
      "resultValue": "Within-order-of-magnitude agreement observed across surveyed literature",
      "conclusion": "Literature evidence deemed sufficient by assessment team to support output comparison factor"
    }
