    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The assessment team concluded that the literature survey of 23 published hemolysis studies provides sufficient supporting evidence for the output comparison credibility factor. The comprehensive coverage of centrifugal pump geometries in the reviewed literature was judged to be broadly representative of the VAD COU, and within-order-of-magnitude agreement across studies was considered adequate. All other credibility factor gaps were acknowledged but deemed acceptable given the early-stage design context. Decision recorded as Accepted on this basis.",
